{"tid":645742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(陶傑爆料) 南亞人籲港嬸讓「關愛座」予阿婆, 反被罵「死摩囉差」","createTime":"2018-04-28T12:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T12:46:06.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"de249ef7e796af0a52caa03bc68560e55580beff","tid":645742,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:18:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/posts/1928189770586870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fposts%2F1928189770586870&d=7n3VMjlbX0LGK%2BTf8D1p7o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6e6a9d67\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/posts/1928189770586870</a><br />\n<br />\n陶傑 Channel<br />\n6小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n美籍香港印裔名記者兼翡翠台新聞雙語評論人禇簡寧( Michael Chugani ) 昨晚九點在港鐵引起關愛座風波。<br />\n<br />\n事源開往將軍澳之港鐵車廂客滿，這位肥胖港嬸佔坐關愛座。一位老婆婆（右圖）與 Michael 俱站立。<br />\n<br />\n新聞評論人發揮專業天性，對肥嬸評論：「你見否這位老人家咁大年紀，可否讓座呢？」<br />\n<br />\n肥嬸拒絕，反駁：「佢又不是傷殘，點解要讓位？」<br />\n<br />\n褚簡寧見狀，企圖用手機將肥嬸尊容拍下，肥嬸抗拒（見左圖），亦用手機反拍，新聞評論人平時上慣電視，Michael 話：「你影我我唔驚，不過你又要俾我影番喎。」肥嬸影完，再次拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n四周乘客微笑睇嘢，見到印度巨星出面維護社會公義，有一個由英國返港之港人看不過眼終於讓座俾婆婆，平息風波。<br />\n<br />\n肥嬸下車時口中唸唸有詞：「死摩囉差。」<br />\n<br />\n至於榮獲名記者出頭義助之婆婆，告訴 Michael :「我今年 91 歲啦，我有睇電視，認得你係名人，多謝你咁有正氣呀。」雙方合照留念，結局甚為溫馨。<br />\n<br />\nMichael Chugani 打電話给我，叫我 FB 報導此事，並悲問：「香港社會點解會變成咁？」<br />\n<br />\n我答：「睇嘢角度唔同少少，香港確實變緊，這位着玫瑰紅 T 恤的中年婦女，竟然有眼唔認得你，至少唔係 TVB 觀眾喎。」"},{"pid":"b1c9f3c4c8cb77cde504902fce1ebf681aaf2d1c","tid":645742,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:19:20.000Z","msg":"註明一下: 印度人亦係南亞裔人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E8%A3%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E4%25BA%259E%25E8%25A3%2594&d=7n3VMjlbX0LGK%2BTf8D1p7o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5d953586\" target=\"_blank\">http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E8%A3%94</a></span><br />\n<br />\n南亞裔<br />\n維基百科，自由的百科全書<br />\n<br />\n南亞裔人士是一個全球各地給予南亞國家的人的統稱，裔的意思是一族人，又可用於一群同一類別的人身上，南亞是亞洲南部的一部分。南亞裔是指原居地為南亞的民族之統稱，主要有來自以下地區的人口：<br />\n<br />\n    巴基斯坦<br />\n    印度<br />\n    馬爾地夫<br />\n    尼泊爾<br />\n    不丹<br />\n    孟加拉<br />\n    斯里蘭卡"},{"pid":"52978c38ff8f4b85953b826e0ce02a6200a6adf9","tid":645742,"uid":83097,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dYqW7UdFDcY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdYqW7UdFDcY&d=7n3VMjlbX0LGK%2BTf8D1p7o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a39df6ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dYqW7UdFDcY</a>"},{"pid":"810d462c4554a53b4aeab6dccb22a7ad046f8c4f","tid":645742,"uid":65400,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"摩囉差 好耐冇聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a954e268e28542ebab7c8f9385ced55f74b39b","tid":645742,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"死阿叉"},{"pid":"096d7e208d7213c570baf9deb8a76a170103f26d","tid":645742,"uid":28397,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"好多新香港人唔知 好多印度人已經幾代喺香港 喺正宗老香港"},{"pid":"05f0f08c0e2eef1b0bca0ccbf888dd506f1b4404","tid":645742,"uid":107231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:28:48.000Z","msg":"關愛座是原罪"},{"pid":"a6103a938564918fa6031e7a47585d880ba9ea47","tid":645742,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"19竟然唔知關愛座hunter文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26912898eaa02e141e4a7441a76b4517fd36